name: Glutamate dehydrogenase  NAD
rxn_str: glu__L_c + h2o_c + nad_c <=> akg_c + h_c + nadh_c + nh4_c

name: Glutamate synthase  NADH2
rxn_str: akg_c + gln__L_c + h_c + nadh_c <=> 2.0 glu__L_c + nad_c

name: Argininosuccinate synthase
rxn_str: asp__L_c + atp_c + citr__L_c <=> amp_c + argsuc_c + h_c + ppi_c

name: N2-(D-1-carboxyethyl)-L-arginine:NAD+ oxidoreductase (L-arginine-forming)
rxn_str: octp_c + nad_c + h2o_c <=> arg__L_c + pyr_c + nadh_c + h_c

name: L-arginine:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
rxn_str: 5g2oxpt_c + nadh_c + h_c + nh3_c <=> arg__L_c + nad_c + h2o_c

name: D-nopaline dehydrogenase
rxn_str: h2o_c + nadp_c + nop_c <=> akg_c + arg__L_c + h_c + nadph_c
